<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/29214420-doughnut-economics"><img alt="Doughnut Economics: Seven Ways to Think Like a 21st-Century Economist" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1631512272l/29214420._SX98_.jpg" />
